803
00:50:57,100 --> 00:51:00,700
Actually, these calls are
our best means of finding this guy.

804
00:51:00,800 --> 00:51:04,000
Every call he makes, every word
he says, to you and to us,

805
00:51:04,000 --> 00:51:05,900
can only provide information.

806
00:51:06,600 --> 00:51:09,800
