826
00:52:05,100 --> 00:52:07,000
Shows what I know, I guess.

827
00:52:20,400 --> 00:52:22,400
...which is why I'm gonna fight this thing.

828
00:52:22,500 --> 00:52:26,200
I am innocent and I have done
nothing except serve the people.

829
